{"tid":1171809,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：會加強向公眾解說逃犯條例修訂","createTime":"2019-05-26T03:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T05:34:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90d3ef7d4edbd972e37a14c178fa6ae4cad5ba9c","tid":1171809,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T03:40:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗發表網誌指，政府會加強向社會各界解說逃犯條例修訂草案，又期望立法會能理性務實就修例展開討論。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗上星期與外國商會講解逃犯條例修訂草案，他指部分與會者了解實情後，明確表示認同和支持修例，認為能夠彰顯法治。<br />\n<br />\n他重申，修例絶不影響現行簽訂的長期協定的安排，政府會加強解說修例內容，並繼續與不同界別團體磋商，澄清誤解及消除不必要的恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又指，政府提出將條例草案直接交上立法會大會審議是為了打破僵局，並非刻意繞過法案委員會，而是迫於無奈的選擇，期望議員能夠理性務實展開討論。"},{"pid":"1929db27db372dd83c00fa105fbcdaae863d96b3","tid":1171809,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T03:40:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=349310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349310&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFCvUjXV925tPaxuyg6D%2B4Js%3D&h=fd86cb92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349310&h=d306f82f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=349310</a>"},{"pid":"a5ef76678ea6d33358c8921639cfafd6eb2b4b48","tid":1171809,"uid":179409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"講條撚咩<br />\n大家就係覺得引渡香港人去人治國家係唔合理<br />\n張建宗你有無可能令中國變成法治國家？<br />\n無就收皮啦"},{"pid":"26f69b70dda193d7c7fdf111f89b9c21dbda7460","tid":1171809,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當你地港豬"},{"pid":"f03975b5d4e74502437d649bc1a00ffc27a61137","tid":1171809,"uid":191462,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"一件事係負面唔會解說多次就會變正面。<br />\nOn9<img src=\"/assets/faces/n